  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Coronavirus (COVID-19): what to do if you’re self-employed and getting less work or no work
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Guidance for people who are self-employed and getting less work or no work because of coronavirus (COVID-19).</p>

  </div>
</div>

